sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant YourApplication as "Your Application"
    participant LinkedIn
    participant PointsDatabase as "Points Database"

    User->>YourApplication: 1. Tries to access "My Points"
    YourApplication->>User: 2. Prompts to "Log in with LinkedIn"

    User->>LinkedIn: 3. Clicks login and authenticates on LinkedIn

    LinkedIn-->>YourApplication: 4. Confirms the user's identity securely

    note right of YourApplication: The application now knows who the user is.

    YourApplication->>PointsDatabase: 5. Fetches points for the identified user
    PointsDatabase-->>YourApplication: 6. Returns the user's points data

    YourApplication-->>User: 7. Displays the protected page with their points